  "title": "Video by thecassiefeed",
  "description": "‼️SAVE THIS‼️ for your next trip to Kuala Lumpur/Selangor! \n\nI’ve been to KL countless times. Each time, I discover new spots to try, here are the ones that made the list this trip. Malaysia is definitely a foodies paradise. \n\n📍 Huen Kee Claypot Chicken Rice\n\n59, Jln Yew, Pudu, 55100 Kuala Lumpur, Wilayah Persekutuan Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia\n(Closed on Thursdays)\n\n📍 Restoran Kin Kin - famous KL Chilli Pan Mee 🌶️\n\nNo. 6, Jalan Perubatan 4, Taman, Pandan Indah, 55100 Kuala Lumpur, Wilayah Persekutuan, Malaysia\n\n📍 Lam Kee Wantan Noodles - Char Siu & Char Siu Pork Rib Wantan Noodles 🍜 \n\nJalan Bunga Tanjung 10A, Taman Muda, 56100 Kuala Lumpur, Selangor, Malaysia\n(Closed on Tuesdays)\n\n📍 大树下炸年糕 Under The Big Tree Fried Nian Gao (not on Google maps)\n\nOpposite Restoran Hong Sang: D22, Gerai Staik, Jalan Bunga Tanjung 10, Taman Muda, 68000 Ampang, Selangor, Malaysia\n\n📍 Nasi Lemak Shop\n\nG10, Oasis Business Center BU4, Changkat Bandar Utama, Bandar Utama, 47800 Petaling Jaya, Selangor, Malaysia\n\n📍 汤圆坊 YUAN (巴生港口汤圆 • 麻薯 @ Taman Paramount)\n\n40, Jalan 20/16a, Taman Paramount, 46300 Petaling Jaya, Selangor, Malaysia\n(Closed on Sundays)\n\nIf you like what you see, follow me for more!\n\n#klfood #kualalumpurfood #localfood #wheretoeatkl #whattoeatkl #klfoodie #malaysia #malaysiafood",
